  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为任务接口做一个甘特图，展示三个ID组（0、1、2）各自的执行时序。横轴用秒来显示，因为每个任务都很短。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ID=0",
        "ID=1",
        "ID=2",
        "axisFormat",
        "dateFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，时间粒度到秒级。那每个section内部的任务是怎么依赖的？是串行执行吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "task dependency"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，每个ID组内部完全串行。ID=0里面依次是8秒、3秒、2秒的任务；ID=1是7秒、4秒、1秒；ID=2是6秒、5秒。注意ID=1的最后一个1秒任务，它要接在5秒任务之后，但5秒任务属于ID=2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ID=0: 8s/3s/2s",
        "ID=1: 7s/4s/1s",
        "ID=2: 6s/5s",
        "cross-section dependency"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，这里有个交叉依赖——ID=1的1秒任务要等ID=2的5秒任务完成？这是刻意设计的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ID=1: 1s",
        "ID=2: 5s",
        "after 5s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这是关键设计。实际场景中ID=1的收尾任务需要ID=2的中间结果，所以写成\"after 5s\"而不是接在自己组内的4秒任务后面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ID=1: 1s",
        "after 5s",
        "ID=2: 5s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我设置时间格式为SS，坐标轴显示为%S。三个section已建好，每个任务用\"任务名 : 标签, 起始, 时长\"的格式，串行任务都用after关键字衔接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat SS",
        "axisFormat %S",
        "section ID=0/1/2",
        "task bars"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "ID=2的5秒任务标签写错了，应该是\"5s\"不是\"after 6s\"。标签是显示名，起始条件才是after 6s。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ID=2: 5s",
        "label vs start condition"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在每个任务的显示标签和实际时间参数都区分清楚了。ID=0总耗时13秒，ID=1因为等待ID=2的5秒任务，总跨度到17秒，ID=2是11秒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ID=0: 8s/3s/2s",
        "ID=1: 7s/4s/1s with after 5s",
        "ID=2: 6s/5s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
